      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:09:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's okay, girl!",
      "zh": "沒關係，女孩！",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ、女の子！",
      "time": "00:09:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It was just an accident!",
      "zh": "這只是意外！",
      "ja": "ただの事故だよ！",
      "time": "00:09:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't blame you!",
      "zh": "不怪你！",
      "ja": "責めないよ！",
      "time": "00:09:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't worry!",
      "zh": "別擔心！",
      "ja": "心配しないで！",
      "time": "00:09:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no!",
      "zh": "喔，不！",
      "ja": "ああ、いや！",
      "time": "00:09:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where is it?",
      "zh": "它在哪裡？",
      "ja": "どこ？",
      "time": "00:09:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom!",
      "zh": "媽媽！",
      "ja": "ママ！",
      "time": "00:09:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look!",
      "zh": "看！",
      "ja": "見て！",
      "time": "00:09:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There's money in Maya's jeans!",
      "zh": "錢在 Maya 的牛仔褲裡！",
      "ja": "マヤのジーンズにお金がある！",
      "time": "00:09:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why is it here?",
      "zh": "為什麼在這裡？",
      "ja": "なぜここに？",
      "time": "00:09:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The lost money!",
      "zh": "丟失的錢！",
      "ja": "なくしたお金！",
      "time": "00:09:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maya!",
      "zh": "Maya！",
      "ja": "マヤ！",
      "time": "00:09:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why did you lie to us?",
      "zh": "你為什麼對我們說謊？",
      "ja": "なぜ私たちに嘘をついたの？",
      "time": "00:09:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry!",
      "zh": "對不起！",
      "ja": "ごめんなさい！",
      "time": "00:09:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I bought a phone with buy now, pay later!",
      "zh": "我用先買後付買了手機！",
      "ja": "後払いでスマホを買った！",
      "time": "00:09:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I didn't have enough money to pay the bill!",
      "zh": "我沒有足夠的錢付帳單！",
      "ja": "請求書を払うお金が足りなかった！",
      "time": "00:10:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't cry, Maya!",
      "zh": "別哭，Maya！",
      "ja": "泣かないで、マヤ！",
      "time": "00:10:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I will give you my savings!",
      "zh": "我會給你我的存款！",
      "ja": "私の貯金をあげるよ！",
      "time": "00:10:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, Leo!",
      "zh": "不，Leo！",
      "ja": "いいえ、レオ！",
      "time": "00:10:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will return the phone!",
      "zh": "我要退回手機！",
      "ja": "スマホを返すよ！",
      "time": "00:10:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't want it anymore!",
      "zh": "我不想要了！",
      "ja": "もういらない！",
      "time": "00:10:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't cry, Maya!",
      "zh": "別哭，Maya！",
      "ja": "泣かないで、マヤ！",
      "time": "00:10:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm glad you are honest now!",
      "zh": "我很高興你現在誠實了！",
      "ja": "正直になってくれてうれしいよ！",
      "time": "00:10:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Credit and debts are dangerous for kids!",
      "zh": "信用和債務對孩子很危險！",
      "ja": "クレジットと借金は子供には危険だよ！",
      "time": "00:10:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Always ask us first!",
      "zh": "買東西前一定要先問我們！",
      "ja": "何か買う前に必ず私たちに聞いてね！",
      "time": "00:10:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Before you buy anything, you must think!",
      "zh": "買任何東西前，你必須思考！",
      "ja": "何か買う前に考えなきゃ！",
      "time": "00:10:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do I really need it?",
      "zh": "我真的需要它嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に必要かな？",
      "time": "00:10:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I got it, mom!",
      "zh": "我知道了，媽媽！",
      "ja": "わかったよ、ママ！",
      "time": "00:10:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad, thank you for forgiving me!",
      "zh": "爸爸，謝謝你原諒我！",
      "ja": "パパ、許してくれてありがとう！",
      "time": "00:10:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, Sarah!",
      "zh": "嘿，Sarah！",
      "ja": "ねえ、サラ！",
      "time": "00:10:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's put our name on our bracelet!",
      "zh": "我們在手環上寫名字吧！",
      "ja": "ブレスレットに名前を書こう！",
      "time": "00:10:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah!",
      "zh": "好！",
      "ja": "うん！",
      "time": "00:10:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where is the letter A?",
      "zh": "字母 A 在哪裡？",
      "ja": "Aの文字はどこ？",
      "time": "00:10:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey!",
      "zh": "嘿！",
      "ja": "ねえ！",
      "time": "00:10:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I got a new Bla-boo-boo box!",
      "zh": "我有一個新的 Bla-boo-boo 盒子！",
      "ja": "新しいブラブーブーボックスを手に入れた！",
      "time": "00:10:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wanna see it?",
      "zh": "想看嗎？",
      "ja": "見たい？",
      "time": "00:10:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No way!",
      "zh": "不行！",
      "ja": "ダメ！",
      "time": "00:10:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's see!",
      "zh": "讓我看看！",
      "ja": "見せて！",
      "time": "00:11:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's see!",
      "zh": "讓我看看！",
      "ja": "見せて！",
      "time": "00:11:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But...",
      "zh": "但是...",
      "ja": "でも...",
      "time": "00:11:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're making our friendship bracelet!",
      "zh": "我們正在做友誼手環！",
      "ja": "私たちは友情のブレスレットを作っている！",
      "time": "00:11:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just a minute!",
      "zh": "等一下！",
      "ja": "ちょっと待って！",
      "time": "00:11:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll be back, Maya!",
      "zh": "我馬上回來，Maya！",
      "ja": "すぐ戻るよ、マヤ！",
      "time": "00:11:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But...",
      "zh": "但是...",
      "ja": "でも...",
      "time": "00:11:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We are...",
      "zh": "我們快...",
      "ja": "私たちは...",
      "time": "00:11:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Almost done!",
      "zh": "快完成了！",
      "ja": "もうすぐ終わる！",
      "time": "00:11:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey!",
      "zh": "嘿！",
      "ja": "ねえ！",
      "time": "00:11:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "それは何？",
      "time": "00:11:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:11:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Drawing on a tablet is so cool!",
      "zh": "在平板上畫畫真酷！",
      "ja": "タブレットで描くのはすごくかっこいい！",
      "time": "00:11:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Perhaps they're old and not modern!",
      "zh": "也許他們老了，不現代！",
      "ja": "たぶん古くてモダンじゃない！",
      "time": "00:11:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mother's Day is coming!",
      "zh": "母親節快到了！",
      "ja": "母の日が近づいている！",
      "time": "00:11:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What are you preparing for, class?",
      "zh": "同學們，你們準備什麼？",
      "ja": "クラスのみんな、何を準備しているの？",
      "time": "00:11:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "哦！",
      "ja": "ああ！",
      "time": "00:11:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I bought a gorgeous bag for my mom!",
      "zh": "我買了一個華麗的包給媽媽！",
      "ja": "ママに豪華なバッグを買った！",
      "time": "00:11:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "With my own savings teacher?",
      "zh": "是用我自己的存款嗎，老師？",
      "ja": "自分の貯金で買ったの、先生？",
      "time": "00:11:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My dad and I bought a hundred roses!",
      "zh": "我和爸爸買了一百朵玫瑰！",
      "ja": "パパと一緒に100本のバラを買った！",
      "time": "00:12:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maya?",
      "zh": "Maya？",
      "ja": "マヤ？",
      "time": "00:12:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What special gift do you have for your mom?",
      "zh": "你有什麼特別的禮物給媽媽？",
      "ja": "ママにどんな特別なプレゼントがあるの？",
      "time": "00:12:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't show them this simple card!",
      "zh": "我不能給他們看這張簡單的卡片！",
      "ja": "このシンプルなカードは見せられない！",
      "time": "00:12:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I...",
      "zh": "我...",
      "ja": "私...",
      "time": "00:12:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめんなさい。",
      "time": "00:12:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I forgot it!",
      "zh": "我忘了帶！",
      "ja": "忘れた！",
      "time": "00:12:24"
    }
  ]
}